		"text": "The Loss of Dalmatia \n\n Dalmatia is lost. The Adriatic coast now belongs to ambitious warlords, opportunistic pirates, and former taxpayers. Historians call this a crisis. Tax collectors call it a disaster.",
		"presentation":"Alert",
		"choices": [
			{
			"text": "Mobilize the provincial elite",
			"uniques": [
				"Instantly provides [1] [Dalmatia P] <hidden from users>",
				"Only available <if [Mounted Focus] is not constructed>",
				"Gain a free [Mounted Focus] [in capital]",
				"Gain [1000] [Gold] <when below [4] [Manpower]> <when below [2] [Horses]>",
				"Gain [2000] [Gold] <when below [8] [Manpower]> <when below [3] [Horses]>",
				"Gain [1000] [Gold]",
				"[1] free [General] units appear <when above [1] [Nobles]>",
				"[1] free [Cavalry] units appear <when above [4] [Manpower]> <when above [1] [Horses]>",
				"[2] free [Cavalry] units appear <when above [8] [Manpower]> <when above [3] [Horses]>",
				"[-2 Happiness, -2 Gold, -1 Production] [in all cities] <for [10] turns>"
				]
		},
		{
			"text": "Fortify the Adriatic coast",
			"uniques": [
				"Instantly provides [1] [Dalmatia P] <hidden from users>", 
				"Gain a free [Walls] [in all cities] <in cities without a [Walls]> <in cities with at least [15] [Population]>", 
				"Gain a free [Wall Towers] [in all cities] <in cities without a [Wall Towers]> <in cities with at least [17] [Population]>",
				"[-3 Gold] [in all cities] <for [10] turns>"
]
		},
		{
			"text": "Withdraw the remaining garrisons",
			"uniques": [
				"Instantly provides [1] [Dalmatia P] <hidden from users>",
				"Gain [8000] [Gold]",
				"[-1 Happiness, -1 Food, +1 Production] [in all cities] <for [10] turns>"
				]
		}
	],
			"civilopediaText": [
		{
			"text": "The Illyrians are back, and they remembered where Rome keeps its money.",
			"link": "Buildings/Dalmatia"
		}
	]
