            {
                "name": "The Loss of Thracia",
                "text": "The Loss of Thracia \n\n Thracia has fallen beyond imperial control. The roads to Constantinople grow less secure, while ambitious warlords and restless tribes compete to inherit Rome's former authority. As usual, everyone claims they are merely restoring order.",
